reviewer: unbraind
risk: high
confidence: 100
sprint: 2026-07-security
release: 2026.7.16
resolution: "Protected master with PR-only changes, nine required current checks, linear history, conversation resolution, and destructive-update blocks."
expected_result: Unverified or destructive non-admin changes cannot enter master; the owner retains an emergency bypass.
actual_result: GitHub branch-protection API returned the requested policy with strict checks and all protective flags enabled.
