comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T17:09:23.324Z",codex-root,gh api repos/unbraind/homeassistant-cli/branches/master/protection returned Branch not protected; repository rulesets list is empty.
  "2026-07-16T17:23:23.081Z",codex-root,"Applied master protection after merge. GitHub confirms strict up-to-date required contexts for Bun/Node quality, coverage, package smoke, commit audit, history scan, CodeQL, dependency audit, and PR title; PR workflow, linear history, stale-review dismissal, conversation resolution, and force-push/deletion blocks are enabled. Admin enforcement remains disabled as the explicit emergency owner bypass."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T17:09:23.324Z",codex-root,Apply protection only after the remediation PR merges so new required checks are known-good and do not block this bootstrap delivery.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T17:09:23.324Z",codex-root,Security workflows do not protect the default branch unless repository policy requires their successful contexts.
