close_reason: Default-branch protection is active and verified through the GitHub API.
body: "## Discovery\\n\\nThe authenticated GitHub branch-protection endpoint reports master is not protected and the repository has no rulesets. This permits force pushes/deletion and does not require the established CI/security checks."
